    "The county table (B-7) reports tax assessed \u2014 a different measure from the tax liability in the statewide bracket table (B-4A). County figures also include nonresident and unallocated returns, listed separately.",
    "ZIP-code totals are published for a more recent tax year than the bracket and county tables, and ZIPs below the disclosure threshold are omitted by FTB."
